==Structure==
Viruses in Barnaviridae are non-enveloped, with icosahedral and  Bacilliform geometries, and T=1 symmetry. These viruses are about 50&nbsp;nm long. Genomes are linear, around 4kb in length. The genome has 43 open reading frames.<ref name=ViralZone />

